y slow, you can then ascend and unlock permanent boosts to your production<br></li><li>Surprise<br></li><li>No spoilers for you</li></ul><br>Yep, short list, hope you get it, a simple clicker idler game with lots of hours and achievements to waste and unlock respectively.<br>Enjoy!",
